  "text": "Preoperative clinical staging and pathological staging were carried out according to the UICC classification (7th edition). The local treatment effect was evaluated by tumor regression grade (TRG) according to the method described by the American Joint Committee on Cancer and the College of American Pathologists. [CITATION_1] [CITATION_2] Other variables obtained from the pathology report were pathological stage (pStage and ypStage), lymphatic invasion (LYI), vascular invasion (VI), and perineural invasion (PNI).",
